rdfs:Resource.rdf:comment: Resource that describes the Topic Models, executed with LDA - VEM. The class for each instance of Topic presents 15 terms most important for a specific Topic and the abstracts linked.
The class Query, its instances are the executed queries. For these reasons this class is cohesive with the class Edge and Nodes.
